QUESTION NO: 1 CORRECT TEXT
Within Workflow Designer, which elements are automatically placed in the Workflow Design space
when a new Workflow is created?
A - Extension
B - Approved
C - Work order
D - Rejected
Answer: A, B, C, D
QUESTION NO: 2 CORRECT TEXT
Which of the following statements are true regarding the To Do List?
A - Users are taken immediately to their To Do lists upon logging in if the list contains one or
more items.
B - Items in the To Do list are grouped according to their activity ID.
C - Access the To Do list from Home > Lists > Access To Do List.
D - Requests in the To Do list remain for predetermined time before being escalated.
Answer: A, B, C, D
QUESTION NO: 3 CORRECT TEXT
Which of the following are valid IBM Tivoli Identity Manager role types?
A - Dynamic roles
B - Integrated roles
C - Stagnant roles
D - Static roles
Answer: A, B, C, D
